Author: hentaigrandma
Text: Literally me rn. Mine takes some weird battery i’m worried will be expensive. Ugh it’s killing me not to know especially since i had a successful day of restricting.

Author: Sunflowersandrainx
Text: Don’t worry. Your weight loss will not be affected by this. You’ll just see how much you weight next time, maybe you even lost more weight than usual since there’s more time in between weight-ins. Can you get a new battery anywhere?
